# Game Collection Manager - SBA318

A small Express.js application that allows users to manage a collection of games.

## Features
- Express server
- RESTful API
- CRUD operations for games
- EJS rendered views
- Custom middleware
- Error handling middleware
- Static CSS styling
## Technologies Used
- Node.js
- Express.js
- EJS
- JavaScript
- CSS
## Project Structure
- routes - API routes
- views - EJS pages
- middleware - custom middleware
- data - application data
- public - CSS files
## Running the Project
Install dependencies:

npm install

Start the server:

npm start

Open in browser:

http://localhost:3000

## API Routes
GET /games

GET /games/:id

POST /games

PUT /games/:id

PATCH /games/:id

DELETE /games/:id

GET /users

GET /reviews

## Purpose

This project was created to practice building a REST API using Express and connecting it with rendered views and forms.